&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Use your expertise to design and deliver technology that will power the next generation of products&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Take cross-team decisions that will influence the Datadog frontend community at large&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Lead through example and excellence, helping the people around you grow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Improve processes on your team, and across the whole of frontend engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
